{"tid":1280504,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實美斯比高普更值得獲得獎杯","createTime":"2019-07-03T04:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T12:44:53.000Z","uid":93783,"like":9,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fc4ca86ecf60c849e6685555dbaf7c663d107c68","tid":1280504,"uid":93783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:01:16.000Z","msg":"美斯為國家隊出左好多力，又為阿根廷放棄西班牙，唔似土耳其人，d非洲人為左獎杯走去做德國走狗，14世界杯被德國-6捧杯，15 16美州杯就輸12碼，上年世界杯就算la,所以希望美斯可以為國家隊捧杯，佢係值得攞一個國際賽獎杯<br />\n<br />\n反而高普係贏得歐聯，有人話佢值得贏歐聯，呢個虛偽的人成日講大話，又話唔花大錢買人，點知用左億幾買後衛同龍門，又欺騙卡里奧斯，又話撐佢，點知一個屈尾十買艾利臣，呢個當球員唔係人的教練值得攞杯咩？所以利物浦我一定唔會支持佢攞英超，因為佢唔值"},{"pid":"6893d8a9022be2c9e4e855b8f74bda03abf5ff88","tid":1280504,"uid":38189,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:09:23.000Z","msg":"美斯當年係西班牙養大，見阿根廷國家隊有歷史先返去想癡獎盃"},{"pid":"1bc9cef2e6badf29dbcc97a039893c0b0927758b","tid":1280504,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"過左兩日情緒又開始大起大落  入立會既義士想同大家講...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1280409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1280409</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"df1de818f0d517f76cc76c7690bd786792225543","tid":1280504,"uid":581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:15:45.000Z","msg":"廢中讓返個歐聯比美斯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6a087d6f956c2d44ca09302b7b3b4f5a14308d","tid":1280504,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:39:31.000Z","msg":"講我地利物浦壞話？<br />\n你食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d316bdcaa389c97a74d45f140ce2bf0c789d66","tid":1280504,"uid":103947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:41:10.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n比番個盃美斯啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b268c1d5bf5370ef5fdd361a6aae8e246e604d6b","tid":